<paragraph id="IFRS02_43B" base="F9035637"><paranum>43B</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRSÂ 2"/><data name="paranum" value="43B"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS02_P0139">The entity receiving the goods or services shall measure the goods or services       received as an <xref base="SL141004" href="IFRS02_APPA.dita#IFRS02_APPA/IFRS02_P0246">equity&#x2011;settled share&#x2011;based payment transaction<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0106"/></ph></xref> when:</p><ol id="IFRS02_L0011" base="F9035639" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p id="IFRS02_P0140" base="F9035640">the awards granted are its own <xref base="SL140998" href="IFRS02_APPA.dita#IFRS02_APPA/IFRS02_P0243">equity instruments<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0102"/></ph></xref>, or</p> </li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value>         <p id="IFRS02_P0142" base="F9035642">the entity has no obligation to settle the <xref base="SL141031" href="IFRS02_APPA.dita#IFRS02_APPA/IFRS02_P0286">share&#x2011;based payment               transaction<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0351"/></ph></xref>.</p>         </li></ol><p id="IFRS02_P0144" base="F9035643">The entity shall subsequently remeasure such an       equity&#x2011;settled share&#x2011;based payment transaction only for changes in non&#x2011;market <xref base="SL141040" href="IFRS02_APPA.dita#IFRS02_APPA/IFRS02_P0292">vesting conditions<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0386"/></ph></xref> in accordance with         <xref id="IFRS02_X0236" base="F9048202" href="IFRS02_g19-21.dita#IFRS02_g19-21">paragraphs         19&#x2013;21</xref>.  In all other       circumstances, the entity receiving the goods or services shall measure the goods or services       received as a <xref base="SL140992" href="IFRS02_APPA.dita#IFRS02_APPA/IFRS02_P0240">cash&#x2011;settled share&#x2011;based payment transaction<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0032"/></ph></xref>. </p></body></paragraph>